de` (line 206) to call the new function\\n\\n### `../TASK-jsonl.md`\\n\\nWrite analysis of the `.jsonl` filename issue for OpenCode/Gemini agents as a follow-up task.\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n```bash\\nmise run fmt && mise run lint && mise run test:ci\\n```\\n\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"9fd3cbd9-5e85-4840-9952-aa58b573b20f\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli_experiments\",\"sessionId\":\"022d9e55-d3e6-4a20-a604-247fa9f6f22e\",\"version\":\"2.1.47\",\"gitBranch\":\"soph/opencode-refactor\",\"slug\":\"typed-fluttering-harp\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01Mk4XFJFZF3HWXdzkMkTe5Q\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":13864,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":29846,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":13864},\"output_tokens\":9,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYKYXvNpJ7AyjMZXMA4nk\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"dfdb66ec-d272-4b30-bbab-5fcb1c96c51a\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-20T15:18:26.849Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"dfdb66ec-d272-4b30-bbab-5fcb1c96c51a\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli_experiments\",\"sessionId\":\"022d9e55-d3e6-4a20-a604-247fa9f6f22e\",\"version\":\"2.1.47\",\"gitBranch\":\"soph/opencode-refactor\",\"slug\":\"typed-fluttering-harp\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01Mk4XFJFZF3HWXdzkMkTe5Q\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Let me start by reading the relevant files to understand the current state of the code before making changes.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":13864,\"cach